title: HEELE Dog Harness, Reflective Dog Harness, with Padded Handle Control, 2 Metal Rings, Harness for Small Medium and Large Dogs, Purple, XL
features: Easy to Put On and Off - HEELE dog harness with adjustable chest belt and 2 fast-release buckles to ensure your dog safety and creates a custom fit for your dog. Size XL: Neck 58-89cm(23-35in), Chest 53-97cm(21-38in).

No-Pull and No Choke Design - No stress on dog's neck, pulling pressure is evenly distributed to the body to prevent pulling and choking. With 2 metal leash rings for safer dog walks. Use the chest ring to stop your dog from pulling on walk and the back ring is great for casual walks, etc.

Easy to Adjust - With 4 easy adjustable strong straps around the body. You can use 2 neck straps and 2 chest straps to offer an ideal fit with extra growth room. No worry about slipping out or choking.

Durable and Comfortable - Made of durable nylon oxford and padded with soft cushion to protect your dog's skin. Breathable and comfortable lightweight mesh lining keeps your dog cool during outdoor activities. Soft sponge padding in chest and belly giving extra comfort and protection.

Safe and Perfect Control - Super bright Reflective Strips ensure a SAFE walk in the dark and night. A soft neoprene padded sturdy handle on the back to help you grab and control your dogs in an emergency, also help it to get in the car or steps. Please DO MEASURE your dog to get the right size before purchase! For more details, please read below Product Description.
